{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the presented modals associated with this view controller and its descendants."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"(mdl_aggregateModals) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"aggregateModals","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@Modals@objc(cs)MDLModalList","text":"ModalList","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/Modals\/documentation\/Modals\/ModalList"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The modal presentation system aggregates presented modals by calling this method. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"default implementation retrieves this value from each of its child view controllers, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then appends any modals presented from this view controller’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ModalPresenter"},{"text":", performing a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"depth-first traversal of the view controller hierarchy.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can override this method to change which modals are propagated up this hierarchy. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you can prevent some modals from being aggregated to the root depending on whether"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this view controller is currently visible. When overriding this method, you may find "},{"code":"aggregateChildModals","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"aggregatePresenterModals","